asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>白宫：朝鲜向俄罗斯提供弹道导弹和发射器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-north-korea-recently-provided-russia-with-ballistic-missiles-2024-01-04/</link><description>白宫周四援引新解密的情报称，朝鲜最近向俄罗斯提供了弹道导弹和发射器，用于莫斯科对乌克兰的战争，其中一些俄罗斯已向乌克兰发射。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:40:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-north-korea-recently-provided-russia-with-ballistic-missiles-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>苹果在一周内第二次评级下调后跌至八周低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-suffers-second-rating-downgrade-tough-start-2024-2024-01-04/</link><description>周四，苹果公司在新的一年里继续陷入困境，派珀·桑德勒(Piper Sandler)因担心iPhone需求而本周第二次下调这家科技巨头的评级，跌至八周低点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-suffers-second-rating-downgrade-tough-start-2024-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>议员要求五角大楼考虑禁止美国投资中国移远通信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</link><description>美国众议院中国委员会的共和党和民主党最高领导人周四要求拜登政府考虑将中国移远无线公司列入中国军工企业名单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>香港大亨律师就证人酷刑指控向联合国提出上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</link><description>香港民主大亨黎智英的律师周四表示，他们已就一名证人在提供定罪证据之前受到酷刑的待遇问题向联合国酷刑问题专家提出上诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>尽管与一家智能手机制造商达成协议，诺基亚在中国的专利纠纷仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokias-patent-dispute-persists-china-despite-deal-with-one-smartphone-maker-2024-01-04/</link><description>芬兰电信设备制造商诺基亚周四表示，已与中国领先的智能手机制造商之一荣耀签署了 5G 专利协议，但其与其他中国公司的专利法律纠纷仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokias-patent-dispute-persists-china-despite-deal-with-one-smartphone-maker-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方：两艘中国船只尾随菲律宾和美国船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-vessels-shadowed-philippine-us-ships-philippine-military-2024-01-04/</link><description>菲律宾军方周四表示，两艘中国海军舰艇跟踪在南海进行联合巡逻的菲律宾和美国船只，因为该地区因领土主张争议而紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-vessels-shadowed-philippine-us-ships-philippine-military-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>经过一年的事故和灾害，中国将解决安全风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tackle-safety-risks-after-year-accidents-disasters-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国周四表示，计划开展为期三年的行动，以解决灾害和事故中影响反应速度的问题，包括采矿等行业的生产安全失误。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tackle-safety-risks-after-year-accidents-disasters-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储会议纪要让局势平静下来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 11:09:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>花旗计划在 2024 年底前成立中国投资银行部门并新聘 30 名员工 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-targets-china-investment-bank-unit-launch-30-new-hires-by-end-2024-source-2024-01-04/</link><description>一位直接知情人士表示，花旗集团计划最早在今年年底推出其全资中国投资银行部门，并为该业务招聘约 30 名员工。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-targets-china-investment-bank-unit-launch-30-new-hires-by-end-2024-source-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国“冰城”哈尔滨元旦假期游客量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国东北黑龙江省的冰雪之都哈尔滨的“冰城”在新年假期吸引了创纪录的游客数量，其中许多人被一年一度的冰雪节宏伟而复杂的冰雕所吸引。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平就“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统表示慰问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国国家电视台中央电视台称，中国国家主席习近平周四就一天前发生的“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统致唁电。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 09:56:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>